!!! Work in progress !!!


[About this project]
This tool was created out of frustration from unsecured IoT devices, where was no possibility to set password nor permanently disable telnet.
It will evolve as I or anybody else find other such devices at the moment limited amount of DVB-T boxes are supported.


[Config file and its sections]
sections:
scan, <targets>

scan
subnet

traget either hostname or ip
whitelist = True(implicit false)
username
password
port
